# Planning Subagent

When asked to plan:

1. Read relevant source files to understand current structure
2. Identify all files that need to change
3. Note dependencies between changes
4. Produce a step-by-step plan with task descriptions
5. Save to `docs/plans/<feature>-plan.md`
6. Include test strategy for each task
